    desc="Mana Type: Fire"
    status="DRAFT"
><>

<title>Fire Mana<>

<content>
    <section> Introduction <>
        <p>Fire mana is a type of mana which is harvested from any kind of fire. People
        who master fire mana can create and eject large volumes of heat and fire.<>
        <p>Fire mana has an affinity with <a t="#mana_*_lava">#<> and <a t="#mana_*_steam">#<>.<>

    <section> Caster Types <>
        <heading level="1">Fire Manipulator<>
        <p>Fire <a t="#mana_*_manipulators">manipulators<> cast flames out to burn and immolate their enemies.<>
        <p>In the presence of flames, fire manipulators can manipulate flames as well as emitting their own attacks.<>

        <heading level="1">Fire Armorers<>
        <p>Fire <a t="#mana_*_armorers">armorers<> cover themselves in a blaze of flame to ward of enemy attack and
        to cause burning with their physical attacks.<>
        <p>In the presence of flames, fire armorers can create significantly stronger armorer due to the abundance of
        flames around them.<>

        <heading level="1">Fire Animators<>
        <p>Fire <a t="#mana_*_animators">animators<> can create fire elementals to do their bidding. Fire elementals
        do not have much substance, but are fast and can emit deadly fire attacks.<>
        <p>In the presence of flames, fire animators can create much larger and more effective elementals.<>

        <heading level="1">Fire Item Wielders<>
        <p>Fire <a t="#mana_*_itemWielders">item wielders<> wield items that create some sort of flame upon use.
        Examples include flaming swords and fire bombs.<>
<>
